The following game data and constants are derived from the Industrialist game and are licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0:

### Covered Files and Data:
- `src/data/products.json`
- `src/data/machines.json`
- `src/data/recipes.json`
- Constants in `src/data/mineshaftDrill.js`
- Constants in `src/data/logicAssembler.js`
- Constants in `src/data/treeFarm.js`
- Constants in `src/data/industrialFirebox.js`
- Constants in `src/data/chemicalPlant.js`
- Constants in `src/data/undergroundWasteFacility.js`
- Constants in `src/data/liquidDump.js`
- Constants in `src/data/liquidBurner.js`
